metadata.name: Gone To Bed
metadata.description:
'Gone To Bed' pays tribute to XCOPY's Don't Panic. 

We see a recently deserted living room. Moon light shines trough the window. A projection flickers across the wall.

As we move to the centre of the room, the frantic series of images reveals to be XCOPY's Don't Panic.

The occupants of this home must have taken advice from this piece and went to bed, instead of stressing about volatility, market, investments and the like.
